    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="upa.00071.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <p>Herb yours <choice>
                    <abbr>rec'd</abbr>
                    <expan>received</expan>
                </choice> &#38; welcomed&#8212;Nothing very new with me here&#8212;have enjoyed the
                past seven weeks hugely&#8212;but am quite ready to go back&#8212;You must be having
                first-rate times there&#8212;Bee was here to see me Monday&#8212;looks
                    well&#8212;Eaton<ptr target="upa.00071_n2"/> is still in Canada, I
                hear&#8212;Some artists here, last evening&#8212;(one of the Morans,<ptr
                    target="upa.00071_n3"/> &#38; wife)&#8212;Herb I suppose you get the papers I
                send you<ptr target="upa.00071_n4"/>&#8212;I am well&#8212;great <hi rend="underline"
                    >Tom Moore Centenary</hi><ptr target="upa.00071_n1"/> here in N Y
                to night&#8212;I have been formally invited&#8212;but shall not attend&#8212;</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">W W</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="upa.00071.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
    </text>
